title: Aye Tha Har
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Burmese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Unpretentious restaurant with simple Burmese menu. Curries 2000 kyat, noodle dishes 1000 kyat, salads and soups 1000 kyat. Juices 500-1000 kyat. Serves alcohol. Located on restaurant row on corner of the road down to New Park Hotel.
streetAddress: Yarkhinnthar Hotel Road, Nyaung U, Bagan
